title: First YT Video - Focus on Improvement

embed.description: Remember to leave a like and subscribe for more content! Click the bell to be notified as soon as a video goes live! This is my first video and I just wanted to introduce myself to you and how i wanna improve. New videos with actual gameplay is coming soon.

body: In this video, I just wanna introduce myself and how I´m trying to get better. I actually climbed from gold 3 to plat 4 promos and maybe I can give you some advices, how you can get better aswell.
